      • getTraceModel

        public FeatureModelToNodeTraceModel getTraceModel()

        Returns the trace model. The trace model keeps track of the origin of transformed elements.

        Building the trace model must have been enabled prior to creating the nodes. As a performance concern, this is disabled by default.

        Returns:
        the trace model
